                            .text-bronze-2.text-8xl.font-serif.mb-2 6-11%
                            p.text-white.text-base.font-medium per annum, paid quarterly
                        .text-white.text-base.mb-10(class="desktop:text-xl", style="max-width: 480px") Tokenized LynxCap bonds offer easier access to yields that are backed by real estate security.
                        a.text-white.anchor-button.anchor-button--white(href="#")
